{"type":null,"faqId":48155,"title":"为什么微信运动不会计步，或者计步数一直不增长？","answer":"<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">有三个因素会导致该问题</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">1.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">微信配置白名单延迟，导致手机型号未进入微信运动的白名单，此时需要重新退出微信然后登陆<span>.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">2.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">微信应用存在读取计步数有问题，导致计步数一直为<span>0</span>或者计步到某个数值以后一直不增长。此时有如下两种处理办法：</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">(1).</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">查看微信是否有新版本，更新到新版本解决该问题<span>,</span>然后退出微信重新登录。</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">(2).</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">先取消关注微信运动公众号，然后重新关注微信运动公众号即可。取消关注微信运动公号方法如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/77245_wogqk.png\" width=\"594\" height=\"1110\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151102094920501001.gif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img border=\"0\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/77246_gdnri.png\" width=\"568\" height=\"1110\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151102094920342002.gif\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/77247_xz8a4.png\" width=\"538\" height=\"841\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151102094920651003.jpg\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">手机版本升级后，由于微信运动服务器的计步策略，升级后的步数没超过升级前的步数会导致维新运动计步数不再增加，直到新步数超过老的步数。但是第二天会重新再计步。</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\">如果您还需要了解微信运动的其他<span>FAQ</span>，建议用户在微信运动公众号中输入帮助，然后发送，微信运动会有<span>FAQ</span>推送：</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/77248_szknl.png\" width=\"548\" height=\"972\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151102094920902004.gif\"></span></p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3800","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1446428708000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":57,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}